00:32:17.120 --> 00:32:20.820
Kakarrot!

234
00:32:34.140 --> 00:32:37.570
Broly! Kau masih hidup rupanya?

235
00:32:44.620 --> 00:32:46.740
Gohan!

236
00:32:49.290 --> 00:32:50.870
Kakak!

237
00:32:52.620 --> 00:32:54.260
Kakak!

238
00:32:54.260 --> 00:32:56.870
Wah, Goten!

239
00:32:58.960 --> 00:33:02.570
Sungguh menakjubkan
