252
00:34:18.580 --> 00:34:20.290
Kakarrot...

253
00:34:28.580 --> 00:34:30.140
Videl!

254
00:35:23.910 --> 00:35:25.190
Kakak!

255
00:35:58.280 --> 00:36:01.540
